# Knowledge Base

This directory contains team learnings, best practices, common patterns, and troubleshooting guides.

## Suggested Organization

```
knowledge-base/
├── patterns/           # Reusable code patterns
├── guides/             # How-to guides
├── troubleshooting/    # Common issues and solutions
└── onboarding/         # Onboarding materials
```

## Content Guidelines

- Focus on "why" not just "what"
- Include examples and code snippets
- Link to related planning artifacts
- Keep content up-to-date
- Consolidate learnings from investigations

## Sources

Knowledge base articles can come from:
- Investigation session findings
- Lessons learned during implementation
- Code review insights
- Production incidents
- Team discussions and decisions
